CONFIG
ServiceConfiguration|Activate|Activate: Assign/establish the case  processing unit,||||
ServiceConfiguration|Configure|Configure: Configure/prioritize card case processing activity,||||
CardCase|Update|Update: Update details of an active card case,||updateCardCaseProcedure||Update details of an active card case
Record|Record|Record: Provide documents/transactions/feedback against a card case,||recordCardCaseProcedure||Provide documents/transaction details for an active card case
CardCase|Execute|Execute: initiate a new card case procedure,||executeCardCaseProcedure||Initiate card case processing 
CardCase|Request|Request: Request arbitration/decisioning for a card case,||requestCardCaseProcedure||Request intervention/arbitration for an active card case
Consolidation|INTERNAL|INTERNAL: Consolidate details and investigate case,||||
Chargeback|INTERNAL|INTERNAL: Initiate/oversee chargeback and adjustments,||||
Arbitration|INTERNAL|INTERNAL: Obtain arbitration for disputes that are not resolved||||
Resolution|INTERNAL|INTERNAL: Undertake resolution tasks, communicate decision||||
CustomerCase|Notify|Notify: Notify interested parties on card case activities,||||
CustomerCase|Retrieve|Retrieve: Report on card case resolution as required,||retrieveCardCaseProcedure||Retrieve a card case procedure report
